---
import Slide from "../components/Slide.astro";
import { currentEvent } from "../events";
---

<Slide>
	<h1>No Hands</h1>
	<p class="subtitle">How a webcam and a few megabytes of ML<br />can see your body</p>
	<p class="event">{currentEvent.name} · {currentEvent.date}</p>
	<aside class="notes">
		Hook: raise a hand and wave at the screen. Nothing happens. "By the end of this talk, that will work — this deck
		will be controlled without touching anything."
	</aside>
</Slide>

<style>
	.subtitle {
		color: #94a3b8;
	}
	.event {
		font-size: 0.6em;
		color: #64748b;
	}
</style>
